    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Wizards who choose to become necromancers specialize in spells from the school of necromancy. Necromancers are some of the only wizards that can use healing magic, but they are best known for raising the dead, undead or otherwise. Skilled necromancers raise a graveguard to serve as their devoted servant. Unfortunately, being followed around by the undead is often the reason they are feared or stigmatized.</p><table data-toc-level=\"3\"><caption>The Necromancer</caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.m8f4FMYWV0F98wGj]{Necromancy Specialization}</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.cHeoheBxXYSmJfbv]{Graveguard}</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.LicdG7YAOX5nGhL4]{Deathtouched}</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.8KhA4zHjC79O8OXP]{Mastery of Soul}</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Cd8XFGk1IQKj67ja]{Necromantic Surge}</td></tr></tbody></table>",
